-Mode-Button_Green-2-E-BIKE-e-gravel-bicycle.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/2021-Pivot-EVault-Power-Mode-Button_Green-2-E-BIKE-e-gravel-bicycle-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/2021-Pivot-EVault-Power-Mode-Button_Green-2-E-BIKE-e-gravel-bicycle-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/2021-Pivot-EVault-Power-Mode-Button_Green-2-E-BIKE-e-gravel-bicycle-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/2021-Pivot-EVault-Power-Mode-Button_Green-2-E-BIKE-e-gravel-bicycle-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/2021-Pivot-EVault-Power-Mode-Button_Green-2-E-BIKE-e-gravel-bicycle-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/2021-Pivot-EVault-Power-Mode-Button_Green-2-E-BIKE-e-gravel-bicycle-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/2021-Pivot-EVault-Power-Mode-Button_Green-2-E-BIKE-e-gravel-bicycle-630x420.jpg 630w\"></a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-251506\">&nbsp;</figcaption></figure><p>The system can be controlled through the integrated Evation Bluetooth remote on the top tube, or you can connect to the system through your smart phone or many GPS computers and wearables.</p><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/2021-Pivot-EVault-093-E-BIKE-e-gravel-bicycle.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/2021-Pivot-EVault-093-E-BIKE-e-gravel-bicycle.jpg\" alt=\"Fazua powered Pivot E-Vault e-bike side profile\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100