EVault-004-E-BIKE-e-gravel-bicycle-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/2021-Pivot-EVault-004-E-BIKE-e-gravel-bicycle-630x420.jpg 630w\"></a></p><p>Dropper post? More compliant rigid post? Why not both? That’s exactly what their ISO FLEX seat post tech offers with the ability to run both 27.2mm or 30.9mm seat post diameters. Between the frame and the post is a a vibration isolating device for compliance, yet the option to run a 30.9mm seat post allows for use of more durable dropper post designs.</p><figure id=\"attachment_251510\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-251510\"><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/2021-Pivot-EVault-Water-Bottle-Mount_Green-E-BIKE-e-gravel-bicycle.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/2021-Pivot-EVault-Water-Bottle-Mount_Green-E-BIKE-e-gravel-bicycle.jpg\" alt=\"Fazua powered Pivot E-Vault e-bike downtube\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/2021-Pivot-EVault-Water-Bottle-Mount_Green-E-BIKE-e-gravel-bicycle.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/2021-Pivot-EVault-Water-Bottle-Mount_Green-E-BIKE-e-gravel-bicycle.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/2021-Pivot-EVault-Water-Bottle-Mount_Green-E-BIKE-e-gravel-bicycle-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/2021-Pivot-EVault-Water-Bottle-Mount_Green-E-BIKE-e-gravel-bicycle-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/2021-Pivot-EVa